components.description:
Producer that executes find MongoDB queries, results returned as JSON Array. Example Filter: Filters results stars greater than or equal to 2 and less that 5 with category of Bakery. Data:      
     [
       { "name" : "Caf Con Leche", "stars" : 3, "categories" : ["Bakery", "Coffee", "Pastries"] },
       { "name" : "Fred's", "stars" : 1, "categories" : ["Bakery", "Coffee", "Pastries"] }
     ]

   Query:      
     { "stars" : { "$gte" : 2, "$lt" : 5 }, "categories" : "Bakery" }

   Result:      
     [ { "name" : "Caf Con Leche", "stars" : 3, "categories" : ["Bakery", "Coffee", "Pastries"] } ]

